partys candidate for chancellor 
kohls conservative christian democratic union was handed the 
latest in a string of local setbacks the free democrats his 
centrist partner in the governing bonn coalition also lost seats 
nationally wellknown and respected as a tough career 
politician lafontaine would be strong opposition in kohls bid for 
a third fouryear term as west german leader 
sundays vote in saarland was an unexpectedly strong endorsement 
