the influx 
the social democrats polled 544 compared with 334 percent for 
the christian democratic union and 56 percent for the free 
democrats 
the environmentalist greens party polled 27 percent short of 
the 5 percent needed to enter the regional parliament the 
ultrarightist republicans making their debut in saarland 
received 33 percent of the vote 
according to preliminary official results the social democrats 
