cheneys list is only a suggestion however since it costs 
money to shut bases down and legislation is necessary to accomplish 
the complex feat the savings are not usually accrued until years 
later 
in actuality cheneys list is a proposal to study which bases 
should be eliminated closing a base also requires a lengthy series 
of environmental impact statements which often lead to delays 
