the proposal saying the impact would be minimal and is necessary 
to save the program from huge loan losses 
he said that since the first 25000 of a loan would be exempt 
from the fee and the usual home costs 80000 the home loan would 
require only a 2200 to 2300 down payment 
the potential is much greater that the borrower will not 
walk away from a mortgage with that much money invested in it 
avent said 
