public health standards he said 
sulfur dioxide emissions are nearly nine times higher those in 
west germany and considerably worse than in czechoslovakia and 
poland which along with east germany are the most polluted nations 
in europe diederich said 
the minister said he would press the government to give the 
environment equal rank with economic performance 
